zes warehouse movements and identifies opportunities originating from the warehouse as well as interfaces with dcs suppliers carriers and stores its software suite also includes delivery and receiving module that analyzes receiving transfers and returns data to identify opportunities originating from the store’s back door interface to the dcs suppliers pl and other stores inventory module for analyzing inventory count rfid and unsellable and stock adjustment data to identify opportunities originating from shrink damagewaste onshelf availability inventory distortion markdowns and sales trends sales module which analyzes cashier and pos transactional data to identify opportunities originating from process failures lack of training cashier fraud coupon abuse and noncompliance during checkout and customer return processes and marketing module that analyzes customer and promotional activity to identify opportunities originating from changes in customer behavior promotional execution and effectiveness as well as impact of marketing efforts on basket size and value in addition it provides mobile field application a solution for retail field users to view their stores’ activities in realtime on the sales floor profitect inc was founded in  and is based in waltham massachusetts detailed description  trapelo roadreservoir placesuite waltham ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwprofitectcom key executives for profitect inc mr guy yehiav chairman and chief executive officer ms stella chistyakov vice president of finance mr yonatan olsha managing director of emea mr will roche senior director mr art dirik chief customer officer compensation as of fiscal year  profitect inc key developments profitect inc presents at nrf protect  loss prevention conference  expo jun  am jun   profitect inc presents at nrf protect  loss prevention conference  expo jun  am venue gaylord national harbor hotel washington united states speakers guy yehiav chairman and chief executive officer jordan rivchun director of loss prevention dsw profitect appoints art dirik as chief customer officer jan   profitect reported the appointment of art dirik as chief customer officer dirik joins the profitect team with a combination and skillset within retail business processes and technology as well as a background in merchandising shopper analytics supply chain and information technology he will work closely with profitects executive team in driving the companys commitment to customer success dirik joins the profitect team after spending the last  years at nielsen and iri where he held various retail analytics technology and consulting leadership positions during his time at nielsen and iri dirik worked to deliver advanced saas solutions in category management and merchandising optimization shopperloyalty analytics on shelf availability osa and machine learning image recognition technology profitect inc appoints art dirik as chief customer officer jan   profitect inc announced the appointment of art dirik as chief customer officer dirik joins the profitect team with a unique combination and skillset within retail business processes and technology as well as an extensive background in merchandising shopper analytics supply chain and information technology he will work closely with profitects executive team in driving the companys commitment to customer success dirik joins the profitect team after spending the last  years at nielsen and iri where he held various retail analytics technology and consulting leadership positions during his time at nielsen and iri dirik worked to deliver advanced saas solutions in category management and merchandising optimization shopperloyalty analytics on shelf availability osa and machine learning image recognition technology with over  years of experience diriks background in customer relations across a broad range of industries and technologies aligns with profitects longstanding commitment to delivering advanced prescriptive analytics 