sident and cofounder omer matityahu  cofounder products profit amplification suite including sales inventory marketing planning and buying logistics and warehouse delivery and receiving omnichannel mobile field application website wwwprofitectcom contents  history  early history   and beyond  customers  references historyedit in  profitect inc released a software solution to computationally deliver solutions they historically provided their customers through consulting using analytics with prescribed actions the profitect suite was created to consolidate the tools into a single platform since then the company has continuously released newer versions of their solution with ongoing improvements early historyedit profitect consulting was founded in december  by david haim and omer matityahu prior to joining the retail market david evenhaim and omer matityahu studied and developed their practice of airline antiterrorism consulting over several yearscitation needed the cofounders started profitect as a consulting firm for security risk loss reduction and prevention their first retail consultations were successful uncovering high value fraud in the supply chain they found that implementing pattern seeking analytics identified challenges retailers were experiencing before they became a bigger issue thus allowing the company to resolve the issue with timely detailed and guided actions  and beyondedit in  profitect moved its corporate headquarters to waltham ma named guy yehiav as the new ceo and relaunched itself as a software company transitioning from consulting profitect developed a saas offering consisting of  modules each focusing on a different area of the value chain all modules use pattern detection technology and machine learning algorithms to interrogate a company’s data to find anomalies these anomalies often indicate areas for profit improvement to capitalize on these profit opportunities profitect sends alerts to the right manager with a with stepbystep instructions in plain language to correct the issue creating the anomalous data since the softwares original development the company has released newer versions of their saas and have made constant improvements so it is user friendly customersedit some of profitects customers include abercrombie  fitch ahold usa delek king kullen sally beauty weis markets factory  woolworths suitsupply among many others referencesedit  a b c profitect inc private company information  businessweek wwwbloombergcom retrieved    progressivegrocerjuly stagnitodigitalmediacom retrieved    a b putting the focus on action in prescriptive analytics  dataversity  retrieved    how retailers are benefiting from prescriptive analytics datanami  retrieved    a b solutions syed m zubair bokhari  xdimension supply chain news best new solutions from nrf  day  wwwscdigestcom retrieved    progressive grocer the profit hub pdf   profitect  crunchbase wwwcrunchbasecom retrieved    a b profitect to highlight its profit amplification solution at retail technology busin newsthomasnetcom retrieved    qa david evenhaim president of profitect  retail gazette retrieved    guy yehaiv executive profile  biography  businessweek wwwbloombergcom retrieved    customers  profitect retrieved   retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleprofitectoldid categories software companies based in massachusettsretailingprofitsoftware companies of israelhidden categories pages using deprecated image syntaxall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from july  navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this 